title: Darwin's Doubt and Intelligent Design - Collection 2
description:
Darwin's Doubt and Intelligent Design - Collection 2:

We have 20 titles in this upload:

-  Anderson - How Can the Human Mind Occur in the Physical Universe (2007)

-  Barrow et al (Eds.) - Fitness of the Cosmos for Life; Biochemistry and Fine-Tuning (2008)

-  Behe, Dembski & Meyer - Science and Evidence for Design in the Universe (2000)

-  Bell - The Hand, Its Mechanism and Vital Endowments as Evincing Design (1834)

-  Denton - Evolution-a Theory in Crisis; New Developments in Science Are Challenging Orthodoxy Darwinism (1985)

-  Fisher - Manual of Natural Theology (1893)

-  Gazzaniga - Human; the Science Behind What Makes Us Unique (2008)

-  Johnson - Defeating Darwinism by Opening Minds (1997)

-  McGrath & McGrath - The Dawkins Delusion; Atheist Fundamentalism and the Denial of the Divine (2007)

-  Midgley - Evolution as a Religion; Strange Hopes and Stranger Fears, rev. ed. (2002)

-  Sarfati - Refuting Evolution (2008)

-  Schwartz - The GOD Experiments; How Science Is Discovering God in Everything, Including Us (2006)

-  Silagadze - Schrodinger's Cat versus Darwin (2009)

-  Stoczkowski - Explaining Human Origins; Myth, Imagination, and Conjecture (2002)

-  Strobel - The Case for a Creator; a Journalist Investigates Scientific Evidence That Point Toward God (2004)

-  Swan et al (Eds.) - Origin(s) of Design in Nature; a Fresh, Interdisciplinary Look at How Design Emerges in Complex Systems, Especially Life (2012)

-  Trimble - Why Humans Like to Cry; Tragedy, Evolution, and the Brain (2012)

-  Turner (Ed.) - The Artful Mind; Cognitive Science and the Riddle of Human Creativity (2006)

-  Williamson - You Are the Music; How Music Reveals What It Means to Be Human (2014)

-  Yahya - Design in Nature (2004)
